scene.message:
Maki: A month ago this was{nl}
such a beautiful{nl}
flower garden...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: ...{wait_fr:60}Oh, sorry...{nl}
I was lost in thought...{nl}
C'mon, let's hurry{nl}
to the castle!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: In our world, this{nl}
was the police station,{nl}
right?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Before the disaster,{nl}
this world must have been{nl}
quite safe - there's no{nl}
police force at all.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...{wait_fr:60}{nl}
You've no business here{nl}
anymore. Get going.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: {ctl07:1},{nl}
you aren't hurt?{nl}
Hm? Why ask so suddenly?{waitkey}{clearbox}Oh, no reason...{wait_fr:60}{nl}
Does it seem strange,{nl}
me saying such a thing?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: That girl earlier{nl}
asked some heavy stuff...{nl}
Got me feeling kinda blue.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
Ayase hasn't seen this{nl}
many trees in forever!{waitkey}{clearbox}Did you know this smell{nl}
is called ozone?{waitkey}{ret}Ayase: ...{wait_fr:60}Hey, {ctl0f:1}.{nl}
Ever seriously thought{nl}
about "the future"?{waitkey}{clearbox}Ayase...{wait_fr:79} eh, never mind...{nl}
Forget it, too heavy.{nl}
Forget I said anything.{waitkey}{ret}
